@page "/timeline"
@{
  ViewData["Title"] = "Timeline";
  ViewData["Description"] = "A holding page for Queen timeline highlights.";
}

<partial name="_PageHero" model='@(("Archive Chronology", "Timeline", "A warm-white vertical timeline for major Queen moments and future archive milestones.", "1970 onwards"))' />

<section class="qz-section qz-section--warm">
  <div class="qz-container">
    <div class="qz-timeline">
      <div class="qz-timeline-item"><div class="qz-card qz-timeline-card"><h3>A band is named</h3><p>Brian May and Roger Taylor are joined by a new singer, who renames the band Queen.</p></div><div class="qz-timeline-year">1970</div></div>
      <div class="qz-timeline-item"><div class="qz-card qz-timeline-card"><h3>The line-up completes</h3><p>John Deacon joins on bass, completing the classic four-piece.</p></div><div class="qz-timeline-year">1971</div></div>
      <div class="qz-timeline-item"><div class="qz-card qz-timeline-card"><h3>A Night at the Opera</h3><p>The album arrives with Bohemian Rhapsody and changes the band's scale.</p></div><div class="qz-timeline-year">1975</div></div>
      <div class="qz-timeline-item"><div class="qz-card qz-timeline-card"><h3>Live Aid</h3><p>Twenty-one minutes that cement Queen as one of the defining live bands.</p></div><div class="qz-timeline-year">1985</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
